===============================================================================
Third-Party Dependencies
===============================================================================

This software depends on:
  - @modelcontextprotocol/sdk (MIT, Anthropic, PBC.)
  - pino (MIT, Pino contributors)
  - zod (MIT, Colin McDonnell and contributors)

No Adobe-published SDKs are bundled; all Adobe interaction is via direct REST
calls against public Adobe Experience Platform endpoints, authenticated via
Adobe IMS OAuth 2.0 Server-to-Server credentials issued by the operator's own
Adobe Developer Console project.


